# 1. Visualisasi Beberapa Contoh Gambar
def visualize_samples(dataset, class_names):
    fig, axes = plt.subplots(2, 5, figsize=(15, 6))
    axes = axes.ravel()
    for i in range(10):
        img, label = dataset[i]
        axes[i].imshow(img.permute(1, 2, 0))  # CHW -> HWC
        axes[i].set_title(class_names[label])
        axes[i].axis('off')
    plt.tight_layout()
    plt.show()

visualize_samples(train_dataset, class_names)

# 2. Analisis Distribusi Kelas
from collections import Counter

def analyze_class_distribution(dataset):
    labels = [label for _, label in dataset]
    class_counts = Counter(labels)
    plt.bar(class_names, [class_counts[i] for i in range(len(class_names))], color='skyblue')
    plt.xlabel("Classes")
    plt.ylabel("Number of Samples")
    plt.title("Class Distribution")
    plt.show()
    print(f"Class Distribution: {class_counts}")

analyze_class_distribution(train_dataset)

# 3. Identifikasi Potensi Masalah
def check_image_shapes(dataset):
    shapes = [img.size() for img, _ in dataset]
    unique_shapes = set(shapes)
    print(f"Unique Image Shapes: {unique_shapes}")
    if len(unique_shapes) > 1:
        print("Warning: Dataset contains images with varying resolutions.")

import os
import random
from PIL import Image
from torchvision import transforms
from torchvision.datasets import ImageFolder
import torch

# Path ke dataset asli
train_dir = 'chest_xray/train'  # Ganti dengan path folder train Anda

# Inisialisasi transformasi augmentasi
transform = transforms.Compose([
    transforms.RandomHorizontalFlip(),
    transforms.RandomRotation(10),
    transforms.RandomResizedCrop(150, scale=(0.8, 1.0)),
    transforms.ColorJitter(brightness=0.2, contrast=0.2, saturation=0.2, hue=0.2),
    transforms.ToTensor()
])

# Fungsi untuk augmentasi dan simpan gambar
def augment_and_save_images(dataset, target_class='NORMAL', target_num_augments=2534):
    # Tentukan folder kelas target
    class_folder = os.path.join(dataset.root, target_class)

    # Ambil gambar dari folder kelas yang dipilih
    class_images = [os.path.join(class_folder, img) for img in os.listdir(class_folder) if img.endswith('.jpeg') or img.endswith('.png') or img.endswith('.jpg')]

    if not class_images:
        print(f"Tidak ada gambar di kelas {target_class}.")  # Debugging jika tidak ada gambar
        return  # Jika tidak ada gambar, tidak perlu melanjutkan

    current_num_images = len(class_images)
    print(f"Jumlah gambar saat ini di kelas {target_class}: {current_num_images}")

    # Hitung berapa banyak gambar yang perlu ditambahkan
    num_augments_needed = target_num_augments - current_num_images
    print(f"Jumlah gambar yang perlu ditambahkan: {num_augments_needed}")

    if num_augments_needed <= 0:
        print(f"Jumlah gambar di kelas {target_class} sudah cukup, augmentasi tidak diperlukan.")
        return  # Tidak perlu menambah jika sudah cukup

    # Menambah gambar augmentasi
    for i in range(num_augments_needed):
        image_path = random.choice(class_images)  # Pilih gambar secara acak dari dataset yang ada
        img = Image.open(image_path)

        # Terapkan augmentasi dan simpan gambar augmentasi
        augmented_img_tensor = transform(img)

        # Convert tensor kembali ke gambar PIL
        augmented_img_pil = transforms.ToPILImage()(augmented_img_tensor)

        # Tentukan nama untuk gambar baru
        augmented_img_path = os.path.join(class_folder, f"{random.randint(10000, 99999)}.jpg")

        # Simpan gambar augmented
        augmented_img_pil.save(augmented_img_path)

        if (i+1) % 100 == 0:  # Setiap 100 gambar yang disimpan, print status
            print(f"Sudah menambahkan {i+1} gambar augmentasi ke kelas {target_class}.")

    print(f"Augmentasi selesai! {num_augments_needed} gambar telah ditambahkan ke kelas {target_class}.")

# Muat dataset asli
train_dataset = ImageFolder(train_dir)

# Augmentasi hanya untuk kelas 'NORMAL' (huruf besar)
augment_and_save_images(train_dataset, target_class='NORMAL', target_num_augments=3875)

print("Augmentation selesai!")

Augmentation selesai!

# Fungsi pelatihan
def train_model(model, train_loader, val_loader, criterion, optimizer, device, num_epochs=10, patience=3, checkpoint_path="best_model.pth"):
    writer = SummaryWriter(log_dir="./logs")  # TensorBoard logging
    best_val_loss = float("inf")
    early_stop_counter = 0

    for epoch in range(num_epochs):
        print(f"Epoch {epoch+1}/{num_epochs}")
        
        # Training Phase
        model.train()
        train_loss, train_correct = 0, 0
        for inputs, labels in tqdm(train_loader):
            inputs, labels = inputs.to(device), labels.to(device)
            
            optimizer.zero_grad()
            outputs = model(inputs)
            loss = criterion(outputs, labels)
            loss.backward()
            optimizer.step()
            
            train_loss += loss.item() * inputs.size(0)
            train_correct += (outputs.argmax(1) == labels).sum().item()
        
        train_loss /= len(train_loader.dataset)
        train_acc = train_correct / len(train_loader.dataset)

        # Validation Phase
        model.eval()
        val_loss, val_correct = 0, 0
        with torch.no_grad():
            for inputs, labels in val_loader:
                inputs, labels = inputs.to(device), labels.to(device)
                outputs = model(inputs)
                loss = criterion(outputs, labels)
                val_loss += loss.item() * inputs.size(0)
                val_correct += (outputs.argmax(1) == labels).sum().item()
        
        val_loss /= len(val_loader.dataset)
        val_acc = val_correct / len(val_loader.dataset)

        # Logging ke TensorBoard
        writer.add_scalars("Loss", {"train": train_loss, "val": val_loss}, epoch)
        writer.add_scalars("Accuracy", {"train": train_acc, "val": val_acc}, epoch)
        print(f"Train Loss: {train_loss:.4f}, Train Acc: {train_acc:.4f}")
        print(f"Val Loss: {val_loss:.4f}, Val Acc: {val_acc:.4f}")

        # Early Stopping dan Checkpoint
        if val_loss < best_val_loss:
            best_val_loss = val_loss
            torch.save(model.state_dict(), checkpoint_path)
            print("Model checkpoint saved!")
            early_stop_counter = 0
        else:
            early_stop_counter += 1
            if early_stop_counter >= patience:
                print("Early stopping triggered.")
                break

    writer.close()
    return model

class SimpleCNN(nn.Module):
    def __init__(self, num_classes):
        super(SimpleCNN, self).__init__()
        self.conv = nn.Sequential(
            nn.Conv2d(3, 32, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),
            nn.ReLU(),
            nn.MaxPool2d(2, 2),
            nn.Conv2d(32, 64, kernel_size=3, stride=1, padding=1),
            nn.ReLU(),
            nn.MaxPool2d(2, 2)
        )
        self.fc = nn.Sequential(
            nn.Flatten(),
            nn.Linear(64 * 37 * 37, 128),
            nn.ReLU(),
            nn.Linear(128, num_classes)
        )

    def forward(self, x):
        x = self.conv(x)
        x = self.fc(x)
        return x

# Konfigurasi dan pelatihan
device = torch.device("cuda" if torch.cuda.is_available() else "cpu")
model = SimpleCNN(num_classes=len(train_dataset.classes)).to(device)
criterion = nn.CrossEntropyLoss()
optimizer = optim.Adam(model.parameters(), lr=0.001)

cnn_model = train_model(
    model, train_loader, val_loader, criterion, optimizer, device,
    num_epochs=100, patience=3, checkpoint_path="cnn_model.pth"
)

import time
import torch
import torch.nn as nn

def evaluate_model(model, test_loader, criterion, device):
    model.eval() 
    test_loss, test_correct = 0, 0
    inference_times = []

    with torch.no_grad():
        for inputs, labels in test_loader:
            inputs, labels = inputs.to(device), labels.to(device)
            
            # Inference timing
            start_time = time.time()
            outputs = model(inputs)
            inference_times.append(time.time() - start_time)
            
            loss = criterion(outputs, labels)
            test_loss += loss.item() * inputs.size(0)
            test_correct += (outputs.argmax(1) == labels).sum().item()

    test_loss /= len(test_loader.dataset)
    test_acc = test_correct / len(test_loader.dataset)
    avg_inference_time = sum(inference_times) / len(inference_times)

    print(f"Test Loss: {test_loss:.4f}, Test Acc: {test_acc:.4f}")
    print(f"Avg Inference Time per Image: {avg_inference_time:.6f} seconds")

    return test_loss, test_acc, avg_inference_time

# Pastikan variabel-variabel berikut telah diinisialisasi:
# cnn_model, resnet_model, efficientnet_model
# test_loader, criterion, device

# Evaluasi CNN sederhana
cnn_model.load_state_dict(torch.load("cnn_model.pth"))
evaluate_model(cnn_model, test_loader, criterion, device)

# Evaluasi Transfer Learning
resnet_model.load_state_dict(torch.load("resnet_model.pth"))
evaluate_model(resnet_model, test_loader, criterion, device)

# Evaluasi EfficientNet
efficientnet_model.load_state_dict(torch.load("efficientnet_b0_model.pth"))
evaluate_model(efficientnet_model, test_loader, criterion, device)

import pandas as pd

# Fungsi evaluasi untuk mencatat hasil
def evaluate_and_log(model, test_loader, criterion, device, model_name):
    test_loss, test_acc, inference_time = evaluate_model(model, test_loader, criterion, device)
    results = {
        "Model": model_name,
        "Test Loss": test_loss,
        "Test Accuracy": test_acc,
        "Avg Inference Time (s)": inference_time
    }
    return results

# Evaluasi setiap model
results = []

# Evaluasi CNN sederhana
cnn_model.load_state_dict(torch.load("cnn_model.pth"))
results.append(evaluate_and_log(cnn_model, test_loader, criterion, device, "Simple CNN"))

# Evaluasi Transfer Learning resnet
resnet_model.load_state_dict(torch.load("resnet_model.pth"))
results.append(evaluate_and_log(resnet_model, test_loader, criterion, device, "Transfer Learning ResNet"))

# Evaluasi Transfer Learning vgg
# vgg_model.load_state_dict(torch.load("vgg_model.pth"))

# Evaluasi Transfer Learning resnet
efficientnet_model.load_state_dict(torch.load("efficientnet_b0_model.pth"))
results.append(evaluate_and_log(efficientnet_model, test_loader, criterion, device, "Transfer Learning efficientnet"))

# Hasil evaluasi sebagai DataFrame
df_results = pd.DataFrame(results)

# Tampilkan hasil evaluasi
print("\n--- Evaluation Results ---")
print(df_results)

# Simpan hasil ke CSV
df_results.to_csv("evaluation_results.csv", index=False)
print("Results saved to 'evaluation_results.csv'")

from sklearn.metrics import confusion_matrix, ConfusionMatrixDisplay

def plot_confusion_matrix(model, test_loader, class_names, device):
    model.eval()
    all_preds = []
    all_labels = []

    with torch.no_grad():
        for inputs, labels in test_loader:
            inputs, labels = inputs.to(device), labels.to(device)
            outputs = model(inputs)
            preds = outputs.argmax(dim=1)
            all_preds.extend(preds.cpu().numpy())
            all_labels.extend(labels.cpu().numpy())

    cm = confusion_matrix(all_labels, all_preds)
    disp = ConfusionMatrixDisplay(confusion_matrix=cm, display_labels=class_names)
    disp.plot(cmap=plt.cm.Blues)
    plt.title("Confusion Matrix")
    plt.show()

# Plot confusion matrix for each model
print("Confusion Matrix for Simple CNN")
plot_confusion_matrix(cnn_model, test_loader, class_names, device)

print("Confusion Matrix for Transfer Learning ResNet")
plot_confusion_matrix(resnet_model, test_loader, class_names, device)

print("Confusion Matrix for Transfer Learning EfficientNet")
plot_confusion_matrix(efficientnet_model, test_loader, class_names, device)
